data.description: Come see this amazing single story home in the heart of Albuquerque.  This home has two LARGE living rooms, FOUR bedrooms, Two Bathrooms, a laundry room and a large two car garage!  The Kitchen is open to the family room and has a built in breakfast bar with a lot of space to seat a large group!  The back yard features a swimming pool (that this seller never enjoyed) and a huge covered patio that is ready for you to enjoy!    There have been many updates over the years and this house is ready for its NEW OWNERS!
